overview: Ningsih, was suddenly possessed by queen of demon on her wedding day. His mother, aunt Marsih, uncle, Aminudin (prospective husband), both prospective parents-in-law, were unable to cope the situation. Pak Kaum, who was summoned, could not cast out the demon. Finally, Mr. Soekardjo succeeded in healing Ningsih after undertaking the conditions requested by Queen of demon. Finally, Ningsih and Aminudin were married.
title: Rong
